title: Pycon Colombia 2017
description:
Pycon Colombia 2017 is the very first python conference in Colombia. The keynote speakers are:

Jacob Kaplan-Moss, Django co-creator
David Cournapeau,  Core contributor to #numpy and #scipy for several years
Eric Holscher, #ReadtheDocs and #WritetheDocs cofounder
Peadar Coyle, #PyMC3 Contributor and Author

Some stats about PyCon Colombia 2017:
4 Keynote speakers
34 Speakers (Rusia, Slovakia , Brasil, Perú, Ecuador, México, Argentina, Colombia)
3 Spaces (2 auditorium, 1 Workshop room)
4 Sponsors
5 Partners
+25 Volunteers

Diverse talk topics: #MachineLearning #Celery #Django #Tornado #Flask #TensorFlow #OpenCV #DjangoCRM #AmazonAlexa #MicroPython #Luigi #Julia #Scikit-Learn #Coala.io #DjangoChannels #Gevent #QT #OpenEdX #Docker

Get you tickets at https://pyconcolombia.eventbrite.com

Follow us:
https://www.facebook.com/pyconcolombia
https://twitter.com/pyconcolombia
https://www.instagram.com/pyconcolombia/

More info at http://www.pycon.co/

title: Jacob Kaplan-Moss - Pycon Colombia 2017
description:
PyCon Colombia 2017 es la primera conferencia de python en Colombia. Jacob Kaplan-Moss, co-creador de #Django y uno de los keynote speakers los invita todos a unirse a está gran evento. 

Adicionalmente contamos con otros grandes keynote speakers como:

David Cournapeau, core contributor de #numpy y #scipy por varios años
Eric Holscher, codundador de #ReadtheDocs y #WritetheDocs
Peadar Coyle, #PyMC3 Contributor y autor
